439
00:18:21.183 --> 00:18:24.061  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:75.93% 
Oh, God, it’s really pounding.

440
00:18:21.183 --> 00:18:24.061  position:15.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:89.66% 
