452
00:18:46.709 --> 00:18:50.295  position:15.00%,start  align:start size:80.00%  line:89.67% 
Mitchell! No.

453
00:18:50.379 --> 00:18:51.880  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:84.33% 
