458
00:19:02.641 --> 00:19:04.685  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:89.67% 
Hey, it’s gonna be okay.

459
00:19:04.769 --> 00:19:06.853  position:70.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:84.33% 
We’re gonna
figure it out.

460
00:19:06.937 --> 00:19:09.648  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:79.00% 
I just want you
to be happy,
and you will be happy.

461
00:19:10.649 --> 00:19:13.277  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:84.33% 
And that is something
worth toasting.

