to avoid past mistakes.

483
00:20:28.310 --> 00:20:30.604  position:20.00%,start  align:start size:75.00%  line:89.67% 
Look.

484
00:20:30.688 --> 00:20:34.733  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
